FEMALE (n= 10 )
. Body fusiform, 151 ( 136–151 ), 68 ( 58–68 ) wide; Gnathosoma downcurved, 19 ( 18–22 ); basal seta ( ep ) 2 ( 2–3 ); antapical seta ( d ) 4 ( 4–5 ) long, not branched, angled as in
Fig. 1
